{"type": "article", "id": 10238, "title": "Portiko 便携式插板", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-01T07:41:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606002646XHOr3jwSsR5YKelz.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t美国设计工作室 Bluelounge 最近推出了一款叫做 “Portiko” 的便携式插板，小巧的插板上在两侧各有一个插座和一个 USB 端口，两侧的分布避免了电源线缠绕在一起，而插板的线有 6 米长，满足多种情形下的需求。目前产品有白色和蓝色两种颜色可选，售价 25 美元。<a href=\"http://www.bluelounge.com/us/portiko\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002645xbXVfr284HK9M1ul.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606060026456NE1XSrpUDxHM5y8.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}